{"id":1744,"category_slug":"toeic","category_name":"TOEIC Listening","position":461,"title":"Conversation 231","subtitle":"Suit Alteration Pickup Inquiry","level":"B1","parts":17,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toeic/conversation-231.1744/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-231-2024-10-25-13-55-38/0-conversation-231.mp3","transcript":"Good morning! This is Harper's Tailoring.\nHow can I assist you today?\nHi, this is Neville Miller.\nI dropped off a suit for alterations last week,\nand I wanted to check if it's ready for pickup.\nLet me check...\nAh, Mr. Miller, it looks like your suit will be ready by tomorrow afternoon.\nWe ran into some delays.\nOh, no problem!\nI wasn't planning to wear it until the weekend anyway.\nI'll swing by tomorrow after work.\nThat works perfectly.\nJust make sure to bring your receipt when you come by.\nThe total cost is $45.\nSure, I'll bring it.\nAnd I assume you're still open until 6 pm?\nYes, we close at 6. But if you're running late, give us a call, and we'll wait a bit.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T21:03:54","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Good morning! This is Harper's Tailoring.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-231-2024-10-25-13-55-38/1.mp3","time_start":0.0,"time_end":1.85},{"position":2,"content":"How can I assist you today?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-231-2024-10-25-13-55-38/2.mp3","time_start":1.78,"time_end":3.36},{"position":3,"content":"Hi, this is Neville Miller.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-231-2024-10-25-13-55-38/3.mp3","time_start":3.55,"time_end":5.56},{"position":4,"content":"I dropped off a suit for alterations last week,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-231-2024-10-25-13-55-38/4.mp3","time_start":5.56,"time_end":8.74},{"position":5,"content":"and I wanted to check if it's ready for pickup.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-231-2024-10-25-13-55-38/5.mp3","time_start":8.92,"time_end":11.5},{"position":6,"content":"Let me check...","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-231-2024-10-25-13-55-38/6.mp3","time_start":11.76,"time_end":12.96},{"position":7,"content":"Ah, Mr. Miller, it looks like your suit will be ready by tomorrow afternoon.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-231-2024-10-25-13-55-38/7.mp3","time_start":13.18,"time_end":17.21},{"position":8,"content":"We ran into some delays.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-231-2024-10-25-13-55-38/8.mp3","time_start":17.21,"time_end":19.0},{"position":9,"content":"Oh, no problem!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-231-2024-10-25-13-55-38/9.mp3","time_start":19.0,"time_end":20.78},{"position":10,"content":"I wasn't planning to wear it until the weekend anyway.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-231-2024-10-25-13-55-38/10.mp3","time_start":20.78,"time_end":23.89},{"position":11,"content":"I'll swing by tomorrow after work.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-231-2024-10-25-13-55-38/11.mp3","time_start":23.89,"time_end":26.33},{"position":12,"content":"That works perfectly.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-231-2024-10-25-13-55-38/12.mp3","time_start":26.33,"time_end":27.83},{"position":13,"content":"Just make sure to bring your receipt when you come by.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-231-2024-10-25-13-55-38/13.mp3","time_start":27.95,"time_end":30.54},{"position":14,"content":"The total cost is $45.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-231-2024-10-25-13-55-38/14.mp3","time_start":30.54,"time_end":32.82},{"position":15,"content":"Sure, I'll bring it.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-231-2024-10-25-13-55-38/15.mp3","time_start":32.82,"time_end":34.27},{"position":16,"content":"And I assume you're still open until 6 pm?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-231-2024-10-25-13-55-38/16.mp3","time_start":34.27,"time_end":37.2},{"position":17,"content":"Yes, we close at 6. But if you're running late, give us a call, and we'll wait a bit.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-231-2024-10-25-13-55-38/17.mp3","time_start":37.2,"time_end":41.22}]}